    <h1>‘Contact Us’ Page Guidelines</h1>

    <div class="publication-wrapper">
      
      <div class="publication-container">
        <section class="lede">
          <p><strong>Summary:</strong>&nbsp;Users still expect to see company addresses, phone numbers, and email addresses on ‘Contact Us’ pages. Don’t hide or replace these elements with automated tools such as ‘Contact Us’ forms or chat.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="authors-and-topics">
          <div class="byline-wrapper">
            
              <div class="authors inline-nav">
                <p><strong>By </strong><span id="gaDataAuthors" class="ga-data-layer" aria-hidden="true">Anna Kaley</span>
</p>
                
